aboutMe.label: Profile
aboutMe.description: Highly skilled full stack developer with over 5 years of experience in developing and maintaining web applications. Proficient in a wide range of programming languages, frameworks, and tools,including React.js, Angular, Vue.js, node.js, PHP, Python and so on. Strong problem-solving skills and ability to work independently or as part of a team. Passionate about staying up-to-date with the latest trends and best practices in web development
